overview: Jadyn is finally back home after being away at school and is eager to spend some special time with her stepdad... even if that means risking getting caught by her mom!  Jeni knows her stepdad is obsessed with her, but this naughty girl doesn't mind; she loves the attention.  Layla is so sick of her mom that she's ready to give stepdaddy everything he wants just to have him all to herself.  Sofie is suspicious that her stepdaddy may have creeped on her and she wants to know just how far he's willing to go!
title: Dad Crush 9
